Text.Value: Tried. But Connor's death... was horrible. Guts... everywhere. Mayrina not... right since.
How did you die?
With pitchforks. Stupid...
What drove your sister to leave?
Looked so... innocent. But the teeth...
Apples... so red... so delicious but... ngh

EditorData.NodeContext: Noise of pain at the end

Text.Value: Maybe Mayrina wants to stay with Ethel?
I found Mayrina's note. Why didn't you stop her?
Little sis'... missing...
She's scared she won't be... a good mum. But... she will. I know it...
Johl... cattle... farmer.
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Course... 'cause she promised... to bring Rina's husband... back. But hags... lie...
Is the food here safe to eat?
How do you know your sister is even here?
Who are you?
Leave.
How do you know your sister is even here?
Why even come here?
*The corpse regards you with unrelenting malice.*
Get her back... get Rina... back...
How did you plan on killing this hag?
The... note...
Kill... ngh... the hag...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

Synopsis: Johl has died either at the hag's or the player's hands. You can speak with him to learn of the hag and Mayrina.
